  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3dd4af88-31d1-4706-8736-bfbf83618352\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:793px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224248855042/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-24938592-8404-4b11-91cb-89854a8d61f4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-290fb151-5883-468b-8f21-e6638f5cb950\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-526c8267-2fd1-4f7c-ad4b-d9849196b070\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8b5b9424-9af3-4785-8342-ae58a7e02c79\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d4adb848-9e36-47f3-820c-9b0f608f87b2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ab236b23-68a9-4aae-b9a9-b4ffc28b80ad\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d893ba55-a38c-4dbd-b9c7-966633f22446\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오늘은 제품의 완성도를 결정짓는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-01227a5d-3a54-4860-88a4-54ef4947c193\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-895d8265-a813-4158-b712-a18320a74bbe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">'작은 거인', </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2310eb4b-e069-4337-a874-ebf435d50e1e\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">크라프트 행택(Hang Tag)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5e903fa5-2974-49f3-a87f-5f74319d2202\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-af24785f-e293-46c0-9cac-30e5eb284afc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인에 대해 이야기해 보려 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e7683b7c-407c-4f96-a666-1c9bd2d8658d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-41c96d5e-92fa-4fc3-aacd-914bef0fb0bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9e1bd1a7-a00f-40ab-8807-01bad26b3b2d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ff62cf5f-c4b3-4f0a-9cab-5fcb48a8e514\" style=\"color:#555555;\">최근 브랜드의 새로운 로고를 담아 제작한</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9c877ab3-5582-4ee9-9095-17d5901a7049\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a47c2eb9-9593-441c-82c6-7735531a53db\" style=\"color:#555555;\">택 이미지를 보며, 크라프트지가 주는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-344d59b0-e4ad-41f6-938c-42df2ca9ef4b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-42cb3b48-0a71-4d18-93d9-51d343ec88df\" style=\"color:#555555;\">매력과 활용법을 함께 살펴볼까 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-397466e8-06ef-487a-a047-a4873d630aa4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0e3d9ea4-52e2-489d-9c60-f7357d4a433b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2cce47a8-a153-4813-a036-9eb2f64a76a5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c79266b1-32de-45e5-8935-0a9e98ce015d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자 이제 시작합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-04ca65f6-92ee-43b2-9713-488eaf0b658e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39f427a1-30a5-42e6-9be2-de7b08adc1cc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-d0a36d88-84aa-4520-b6f4-a0910864bef4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-56fcb0a0-5788-49a2-bc1f-2ce12872e342\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b062b9a1-203c-47b2-9d82-de3effa4ca59\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">시작 전 결론 먼저</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-55e14649-7a84-44aa-aee4-ffe298570f59\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-73d02f71-af64-4fed-95b3-6ba136389533\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-33e0e7b5-86d6-4861-9a42-d6f0ef751481\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 분은 바로 문의주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5e21ee18-7d55-43c7-8c28-76bc10075870\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4fe73b2d-f82c-423c-b14e-89ee06d8f6f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6a442887-a0ef-4244-804e-5d381ebbf4d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a946f75c-0d28-4319-84d2-15b0a948db1f\" style=\"color:#36851e;\">□ 친환경 제품인데 크라프트지 행택을 처음으로 제작하시려는 회사나 개인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9304b04d-61a9-4bae-adba-43700057ce6e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-119743bc-d68e-47ff-b191-981f12eb60d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-07cdc2cf-445c-4e7a-863f-1431eecd04b9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0a328a10-0213-461b-ae0d-e5dbfe6f3d8f\" style=\"color:#36851e;\">□ 크라프트지 인쇄 시 주의할 점을 몰라 인쇄사고가 일어난 고객 또는 걱정되시는 고객님</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-964b5355-9157-465e-8b0a-42f9abed5f59\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9141feb8-281d-402c-874d-eeec0c7316f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4057539c-6df2-4948-872d-a67017946b46\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c3ca03f3-6991-42c9-9f6e-91bcd49a117e\" style=\"color:#36851e;\">□ 모양택에 대한 정보가 없어 그냥 사각 재단으로만 주문하고 계신 고객님</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bfbd7b70-4b6e-4856-ad05-9c0b26faff31\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6b479f9e-3ba4-4e40-9d15-d87e80cb79d1\" style=\"color:#36851e;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0c1b6c0a-a178-4338-b611-b00b1e7819ec\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ca8f6578-d0cb-471f-823e-d8042142715c\" style=\"color:#36851e;\">□ 소량 발주를 하고 싶은데 100개 이하 주문이 가능한지 궁금한 고객님</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8b0604fa-10d1-41f3-a5eb-a4593c555921\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-03d145bf-f61b-4f33-8b32-51897a3a4b37\" style=\"color:#36851e;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c4c2e9f5-2aa5-4929-a78d-64b122a75a7c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bfe7f967-93ff-4c2e-ac13-cb3c018278dd\" style=\"color:#36851e;\">□ 납기나 부자재에 대해 궁금하신 고객님</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35373d9a-3826-4ceb-80e3-fd5f3fe9e492\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d46bf65f-8028-495f-85a7-11c3541f441b\" style=\"color:#36851e;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-821f2845-25bf-40b3-b685-0505acd0418c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224248855042/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5b8260e8-cd19-488f-a7a5-921980db0640\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-400b406c-187d-4f23-aa79-63d360f5ae2e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9bf45c0e-4c07-4c2c-9e17-f5b5021b9216\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">이런 업종에 강력 추천합니다!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d55446c0-adc2-4a91-bffd-1ebe46eb8b61\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bbe9ed41-cc61-4d99-add4-aa5143c0eaf8\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-37670deb-ff3a-4721-91e5-4996f0741583\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-670aafeb-8fb1-4caa-9ac2-06237c4242e9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">크라프트 택은 특유의 따뜻하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a39ea12b-3d71-4f4d-b85c-d883c118351f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d3ca8a8e-2cf7-4534-b8c9-6f2efca006fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">거친 질감 덕분에 특정 업종에서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ee6cf725-654e-4cbf-9507-0d46e6014c33\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-435cae33-2312-47f0-b740-3d0a6e487e5d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">브랜드 아이덴티티를 확고히 하는 데</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4e7283a5-b5bc-414f-a5c2-f1aabe873ead\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d14552bf-35bd-4539-8a20-440ee07acdcc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">큰 역할을 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8119d8c3-c5ee-49d5-bb4a-21669cb7fbdd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2e1d6386-30d1-4c84-b579-d6008dfdef25\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d48848d3-a3fb-4915-b16d-49b11a6893dd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-652d2e06-40c2-4c3e-93ec-fc6962ec90e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>F&amp;B (요리 및 외식업)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e411ba26-d91b-4bbe-8ad9-c179d716dcb8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-08e6f6e6-5b46-4da6-8966-aae5a3f48f8a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">요리사 모자나 조리 도구 로고를 활용해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3c639e8c-5f00-4dac-a17b-d956ec716c4e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-523c6b88-8f12-4869-9efa-3d6facaed6b5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수제 소스, 밀키트, 또는 수제 디저트에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-17fd2006-940a-419c-b5ea-136570b366be\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f1a4a83c-06bf-44bc-a518-63ad79153c04\" style=\"color:#555555;\">부착하면 '정성껏 만든 요리'라는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-83fb5e83-dd08-44c8-8f42-fc8bba5c730b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0f77e4d7-0277-47ff-86d1-c2670f4efb27\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인상을 줍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3db6cd05-dcd0-467b-9060-7d53bf6ae1e9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39330795-f034-4d86-bb0d-c144f29cb1e5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fc7561fa-5a78-4dba-8aa7-64c0db1ce6c9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8c899eb5-7718-4278-937f-530f473ad764\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>주류 및 카페</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-04ded0ae-7114-438c-98ad-673c7607a10e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-969cd58e-45dd-49a8-a1a5-0c89b0ff1737\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위스키, 와인, 수제 맥주나 원두 패키지에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d67fb904-71a5-4bad-91f0-5862e4eb4e4f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e8948ebb-15fc-4cc3-815e-138f39613a87\" style=\"color:#555555;\">'테이스팅 노트' 섹션을 넣어</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bf979035-ff0b-4556-9487-90f641723259\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-320eefe8-a633-4d6f-a338-404bb6209114\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객이 직접 맛을 기록하게 함으로써</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-57d72a02-7237-4002-9f22-2169131eb133\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a2096afd-05dc-4c8b-863a-a79ec7e2b7de\" style=\"color:#555555;\">특별한 경험을 제공할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-da79d804-f03d-481e-ad6a-c2bc65c1e065\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-734b81ef-391d-43ab-a7b2-d94081c1a204\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0338fbb1-9932-48e0-aa91-961722b8b0aa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7b591527-bd6d-482e-8bbc-71a35b8139e1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>핸드메이드 소품</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6eb4d686-8179-470e-9a43-14f0ec3c5d30\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8f888da9-6ce0-4097-a853-0cd4885f0b71\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가죽 공예, 향수, 수제 비누 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7e26f1ac-76d0-4c7f-a341-557288468c0c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8ef32364-d7f9-482e-8a35-176c8f5c4131\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자연 친화적인 이미지가 중요한 브랜드에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7e6d2e3c-f3c8-4c24-987f-90c449821c56\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0183242e-68f3-4150-9fa4-4043b4199a17\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안성맞춤입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-69586b4a-ae8b-42e4-afd5-77ccbc07d183\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ad93d7f2-d66b-47b7-ada6-dd56be903146\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2ce1b522-44a5-436e-9347-b82d2ba57597\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5ebba722-17f9-4631-b879-fa88df44d8e5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>친환경 패션 브랜드</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a1074734-5731-4282-9c97-42d2a48a1b02\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5ef9ea56-ddce-4e6f-93bd-f5e63d60aac7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가공되지 않은 느낌의 크라프트지는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ad4f5044-6907-4ab3-bc36-07f67811c6f8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bc0ab44b-e2e4-41c6-8e5d-4699631a2d23\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에코 중심의 의류 브랜드와</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3d12fc92-c986-4531-965b-e5e35b2cfaa0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ba582620-b7e7-4408-9c41-e9b6fc7c1cea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">찰떡궁합을 자랑합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-141e75f8-d216-4074-ab86-03567d8581f6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224248855042/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-59a54fd2-ef00-4db6-84d8-079df6809767\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e2702095-cc06-483d-80b8-1bf8b3968164\" style=\"\">자유로운 모양택</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5c37166e-4e9c-4bc4-9748-13bde4a80492\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-09d24aa3-7780-41e7-bd93-986da1455c71\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-18a6e6b9-56d4-457f-bb02-9eaa41f5c102\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-78b07ff2-d233-43e1-9673-89f77524b4c2\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">크라프트 택의 거부할 수 없는 매력</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5d3c7501-c862-4961-84e9-2bcf8e563f84\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-25788c67-5099-4a5a-8e65-fea136fa3335\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3f56caf1-2d52-4642-a6de-7e1696f5a7d3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a8fdac9e-1c0d-4271-a9fd-971a874e16ce\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>아날로그 감성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4622ba87-3e26-474e-8284-97e23799b034\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d16d043b-63f8-43e2-a7c2-8aedfb70ba4d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 시대에 손으로 만져지는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-38640846-c5df-4e67-adbc-d7678b4d83ec\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1a637981-1683-4dbc-9f4e-487f42351a33\" style=\"color:#555555;\">크라프트지의 질감은 고객에게</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a2031ba5-c8c7-46b4-9c05-d47d5e208225\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-89790759-1b1f-436c-be5b-f735c00f6533\" style=\"color:#555555;\">시각과 촉각을 동시에 자극하는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3b6bf2f1-3a6f-4be8-bae3-d0f754018e99\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9fd75edd-8fa1-4988-b467-960d54e264c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">따뜻한 경험을 선사합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6fae6c6f-70a7-4b76-8c05-f8d8316a4640\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c6dc0235-ff3c-46d2-b0fd-2599d88eff12\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3ba30fc4-553f-4043-aa46-0942397cc5b3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-57ee9c80-819c-445e-bf0b-852330f84084\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>높은 활용도</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3fdc26ad-f89c-40ba-97e1-27c26f0f7b63\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b276ad02-3c75-4bdc-97a7-31725aecbe14\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이미지를 보시면 아시겠지만,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ff4a187a-29f9-45c4-9b00-013696e23ed7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-62287fd4-bb64-47b0-b5c4-b045141bae35\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객과 소통하는 도구로도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-845a0e11-ab78-4417-a847-c6d626481938\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bb2a7854-38c9-43a9-8f6d-a1bc5429f8fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">활용이 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-761b8a1c-542a-43a9-983a-6ff8d1b0930b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7831159b-a050-465b-9b2c-2178d0263ca0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0d67c46c-8ed0-423f-a2d3-dd3214bff2a2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0a123383-6bef-430b-9da5-927fedfee948\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>지속 가능성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4eafff0d-e93b-4c59-8413-157617fb871a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a2cba0c7-9148-4623-a8d3-8605b9b8f40a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">재활용 종이 느낌을 주는 크라프트지는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-569648b4-1e3c-4a05-b020-81cc1eed71b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-af09645a-f5ec-46c2-9893-594c2908c644\" style=\"color:#555555;\">환경을 생각하는 브랜드라는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6740914c-a418-4a04-87ec-30f463d47747\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-977414a4-8729-42cb-8dd0-547ba8e7b005\" style=\"color:#555555;\">긍정적인 이미지를 구축하는 데</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6682a187-c61d-488b-9bee-fca4c93de395\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6b817c95-726d-402d-ba0b-35f82290a7f4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">도움을 줍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2faa131b-78a9-4fac-ae78-c154a4aa7e43\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224248855042/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-39cfb670-8ae9-4af1-a395-d63aab93b840\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-076a1939-a2de-4817-84cf-d37c9b7ca054\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-da988047-55c7-4f6d-b237-5a8c29df325c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-928e86f8-8ac7-45dc-b79f-5afbbad6b1bd\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">제작 시 꼭 확인하세요! (주의 사항)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c32942af-a82e-4dd7-81f0-c3e90625eda2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-74d4b112-311d-457a-8324-f5d89f3810b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">크라프트 택은 매력적이지만,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-28394b50-8810-4f91-9fe7-6da156fd787f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e2c56541-7a94-409f-949f-e6da5b0bb387\" style=\"color:#555555;\">재질의 특성상 제작 시 주의해야 할 점이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a74a6c74-ff9b-4c93-8fba-e057f3fa8880\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-87d4131d-399c-4eeb-9f7c-3924591d353c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">몇 가지 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2bad2b5c-739c-4081-bf38-f40c97413131\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4488f321-ddbc-4cf3-b647-8815b2f3da50\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c68dd50c-2188-41df-a562-2b72e9cea4da\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ae26fe07-eee2-4180-8697-f6346fc24431\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>색상 표현의 한계</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-36ce812c-3030-4500-8363-bed5e88068b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a08d0148-d551-446d-80f6-23a00e6a8a75\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이 자체가 갈색 톤을 띠고 있어,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-591dd508-3cb5-437a-b9bd-cfa12b4a3192\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9fa2ddfa-12b9-42e4-9d89-9a390cea087e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">밝은 노란색이나 형광색 등은 색이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-17dd2399-af2d-4868-9868-10d3f1a38e64\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-73a45798-afcc-4706-acba-52cac881eb71\" style=\"color:#555555;\">묻히거나 다르게 보일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3d6537db-6797-4c91-830c-bcaa5d4bed11\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bd2d688a-c200-474f-a717-52cc509ebae7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">검은색(K100)이나 짙은 원색을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2195dfd5-640a-41cc-a0da-e66850e4951f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9de50a75-6a9a-4720-aadd-851e04fabff5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사용하는 것이 가장 깔끔하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4ec0f944-b6ea-4124-8be8-ea31709a9fd5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d3933dce-f522-4c81-b7ed-2bf8cc657869\" style=\"color:#555555;\">선명하게 나옵니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1b933aad-f7b5-4a9e-9ea1-15d27a2d351d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224248855042/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-726e52a0-78ac-46d1-a1dc-f4e222ba183c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e67d8fce-7b42-4b4a-880c-1d2d96cc09f4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ded82c20-dcc3-4fe6-93d4-7a1dce7939cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-410a894e-3979-4668-af9d-a7035942b36f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b75c2ec4-2521-4012-80d7-2bd48c1a497e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>잉크 번짐 주의</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3d8df4bc-6ff3-4d00-97ad-bd6cf0afff74\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-01242f7e-a0a2-43ed-b2af-931d38bcf031\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이 결이 살아있어 아주 미세한 글씨는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dbaf1d62-0121-4c2a-8cee-b9acb4f87ad2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-979576c9-edcc-4b3e-85a6-97e601a3e2f1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄 시 뭉칠 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a8c4c2fb-b19c-4884-8d9a-314b9638fd5b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e76f9fab-6b32-409f-a6bb-4c05ec8926a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가급적 가독성이 좋은 굵기의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f78f69a5-2359-4935-a316-6683961c946b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-23d47ebd-2956-49c9-ac61-e356a2dc8745\" style=\"color:#555555;\">폰트를 권장합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-40feb4c4-9379-4f7f-9b8c-cafe2da7b522\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a16bbb4c-4e60-4ddb-8fc8-d6b12a1ad259\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2e2648ce-c4bd-46a1-8149-009f1da7b399\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-53a3888c-ac8f-4885-aee6-95e0a103169d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>습기에 민감</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-452d4955-9a73-48f6-901d-d026e1f02dd7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c0bd52f7-3a54-414b-b036-90336e998c1e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일반 코팅지에 비해 습기에 약하므로,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3acce7a4-d3de-406a-ad4d-99bf631724d0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-225d30c1-e2c8-4012-aeda-d25ed4e73d67\" style=\"color:#555555;\">냉장 보관이 필수인 제품에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6158d100-6265-45a8-b802-034c8d79ae5b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d3a40d0-c00e-4dd2-b9c4-73c0db5ac110\" style=\"color:#555555;\">직접 닿는 용도로는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-57c02303-8d75-4d7a-9d87-835942e89763\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-31697670-bcd3-48ba-a9a9-193970466550\" style=\"color:#555555;\">적합하지 않을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-45a3a030-c170-4f4d-9097-3c8ca7bdb12c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-88ef7b04-7e3b-4767-ac14-23350d499cc5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F224248855042#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
